Package: sumstat
Title: Summary Statistics for a Numeric Column in a Data.frame
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Colton",
           family = "Stevens",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "colton04@student.ubc.ca",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package provides a function that takes in a data.frame and a numerical column in that dataframe and outputs a data.frame of summary statistics (mean, median, max, min, standard deviation, and count), as well as a histogram of that column's distribution with a vertical line representing the mean.
